## Installation

### Vendor Dependency (Recommended)
1. Download the `MWLib.json` file attached to this release
2. Place it in your robot project's `vendordeps/` directory  
3. Refresh your Gradle project

### Manual Installation
```gradle
dependencies {
    implementation 'com.marswars.frc:MWLib-java:{{ TAG_NAME }}'
}
```
